text:
I love having dinner here! This place is like a premier hawker center.
Personally, I prefer to eat indoors always.
In that sense, this place is good for me while providing multiple food options.
I've tried the Thai, Vietnamese, and Burger shops. All of them were excellent. The prices are reasonable, and the environment is clean and cool.

First time trying Papadum as Burger buddies had closed.
Chicken tikka masala was great! Owner gave some extras as he said there was not enough left of my original order.

Didn't know such place existed till recommended. Had Vietnamese food.  Nice.  Set congress with 2 freshly made spring roll. Nice environment to hang out with friend after a hectic work day,  over drinks. Recommended.

Nice atmosphere at night. If live nearby is a good choice, there are many options, including Chinese, Thai, burgersâ€¦. and food is good as well

Outdoor seems pets friendly, many cute dogs around :))

will come again and try other food!

Nice place for a meal or drink.
Got some good option from Pizza to Thai
